<number pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="5.0" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="4.0">4– 6</number>
) and three pairs of adanal (
<number box="[471,514,1764,1789]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="5.0" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="4.0">4–6</number>
) setae thin, smooth. Genital plates with two genital setae on anterior edge. Adanal lyrifissures located close and parallel to anal plates. Distance 
<emphasis box="[882,910,1800,1824]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">ad</emphasis>
<number box="[910,918,1814,1828]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="1.0">1</number>
– 
<emphasis box="[932,960,1800,1824]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">ad</emphasis>
<number box="[960,968,1814,1828]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="2.0">2</number>
shorter than 
<emphasis box="[1129,1157,1800,1824]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">ad</emphasis>
<number box="[1156,1164,1814,1828]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="2.0">2</number>
– 
<emphasis box="[1178,1206,1800,1824]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">ad</emphasis>
<number box="[1206,1214,1814,1828]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="3.0">3</number>
. Setae 
<emphasis box="[1305,1333,1800,1824]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">ad</emphasis>
<number box="[1333,1341,1814,1828]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="3.0">3</number>
inserted laterally to 
<emphasis box="[284,320,1838,1862]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="577">iad</emphasis>
. Postanal porose area absent. Ovipositor size: 
<number box="[859,900,1839,1863]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="118.0">118</number>
× 
<number box="[935,966,1839,1863]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="24.0">24</number>
; blades (
<number box="[1070,1099,1838,1863]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="41.0">41</number>
) shorter than length of distal section (beyond middle fold; 
<number box="[482,513,1874,1899]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="77.0">77</number>
). Each of three blades with four straight, smooth setae, ψ 
<number box="[1156,1164,1889,1903]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="1.0">1</number>
≈ τ 
<number box="[1201,1209,1889,1903]" pageId="6" pageNumber="577" value="1.0">1</number>
